title: Kurri Kurri Co-Op Society Flora and Fauna
description:
Kurri Kurri Co-Op members privately own and manage a 32 hectare block of remnant vegetation in the Naringal East area. Shares are still available and new members are needed to maintain the co-operative into the future.
See Web Site: www.warrnambool.org/kurrikurri
